CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 18, 1961, pg. A14 reads: "Kappa Karnival Guests got a real bang out of the party held at the Anchorage, last Friday night...-Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Two men, including Samuel W. Lawler II wearing Kappa Alpha Psi fez, and three women, including Helen Smith wearing dress with lace overlay, and Mildred Lawler holding cigarette, seated around circular banquet table with bottles, in the Anchorage for Kappa Alpha Psi's Kappa Karnival
